Eishoi e Ruben


1   Kulo ile ishoi e Ruben ilo kikau le Israel, (ore enkaraki natijing'a enkaji e papaai lenye, meekure eikenari aajo olkikau. Ore erishata enye neishori ilayiok le Yosef olayioni le Israel. Amu eitu eigeri enkarna enye te mbuku oo iishoritin anaa olkikau. 
2   Ore hoo naa Yuda apa ogol alang ilalashera lenyena, naa ninye eimu ilo kitok, kake ene Yosef enjung'ore o lkikau.) 
3  Ore ilayiok le Ruben ilo kikau le Israel naa: Hanok, o Palu, o Hesron, o Karmi.


4  Kulo ilayiok le Yoel: Shemia olayioni lenye, o Gog olayioni lenye, o Shimei olayioni lenye, 
5  o Mika olayioni lenye, o Reaia olayioni lenye, o Baal olayioni lenye, 
6   o Beara olayioni lenye, laa ninye apa eewa olaiguanani Tilgat Pilnesa le Asiria te yararoto. Ninye apa oltung'ani kitok too le Ruben. 
7  Ore iltung'ana lenye too lmareita lenye, ina kata pee eigeri iiishoritin enye naa: ore olkitok lenye naa Yerel, o Sakaria, 
8  o Bela olayioni le Asas, olayioni le Shema, olayioni le Yoel, apa omanya Aroer ometabaiki Nebo o Baalmeon. 
9  Etobiko sii apa te nkalo o loo saen ometabaiki olpolosie lo lpurkel tena shoto e Frati, amu etoponari apa nkishu enye te nkop e Gilead. 
10  Ore too nkolong'i e Saul neitayunye iltung'ana le Hagrit olarrabal, neibung ninche, nebik ninche too lng'oborri lenye te nkop pooki e Gilead te nkalo oloosaen.

Eishoi e Gad


11  Etamanya apa ilayiok le Gad aatashare ninche te nkop e Bashan ometabaiki Saleka. 
12  Yoel apa olkitok nesujaki Shafan o Yanai o Shafat te Bashan. 
13  Ore olorere lenye te risioroto oo nkajijik oo loo menye naa: Mikael, o Meshulam, o Sheba, o Yorai, o Yakan, o Sia, o Eber, lelo pokira oopishana. 
14  Kulo apa ilayiok le Abihail olayioni le Huri olayioni le Yaroa, olayioni le Gilead, olayioni le Mikael, olayioni le Yeshishai, olayioni le Yohado, olayioni le Buus; 
15  Ahis olayioni le Abdiel, olayioni le Guni ninye apa olkitok te nkaji e menye; 
16  nebik apa ninye te Gilead, tiatua Bashan o too nkang'itie enyena, o teina kop pooki nairritishoreki e Sharon o meiting'ie. 
17  Eigeroki apa kuna baa pooki anaa iishoritin too nkolong'i e Yotam olaiguanani le Yuda o too nkolong'i e Yeroboam olaiguanani le Israel.

Njorin oo loshon le nkalo oloosaen


18  Ore tiatua iloshon le Ruben ore Gad o lpisiaai lo losho le Manase, neeta iltung'ana magil, oata long'oi o lalema, neeta nkai, naa arriyiak to larrabal, naa nkalifuni artam oong'uan, o iip naapishana o ntomoni ile, neterretenate ninche te nkisiaayiare. 
19  Neitayu ninche olarrabal o Lhagri, olyetur, Olmafish, Olnadab; 
20  ore ake pee eng'amu ninche eretoto pee egilunore ninche, ore Ilhagri, o lelo pooki ootii tenebo ninche neishoori aapik nkaik oo le Ruben, amu Olaitoriani eishirakitia ninche to larrabal, neisho ninche Enkai eomonunoto enye enkaraki naisiliga ninche ninye. 
21  Neya ninche nkishu enye, o ntamesin enye nkalifuni onom, o nkerra nkalifuni iip are o onom, o sirkon nkalifuni are, o ltung'ana ooishu nkalifuni iip nabo. 
22  Amu eirragaitie ilkumok etuata, amu ore ilo arrabal naa ole Nkai. Nebik ninche te nkop enye ometabau eyararoto.

Iltung'ana le nkalo oloo saen le Manase


23  Ore olpisiai loo ltung'ana le Manase nebik teina kop, neaku ninche kumok oleng te Bashan o metabaiki Baarhermon, o Senir, o ldoinyio le Hermon. 
24  Kulo apa ilukuny oo nkajijik oo loo menye: Efer, o Ishi, o Eliel, o Esriel, o Yeremia, o Hadafia, o Yadiel, lelo murran magil, ooning'o, laa lukuny oo nkajijik oo loo menye.

Etaarayioki aaipang'ie iloshon lo loosaen


25  Kake etogolong'okita ninche Enkai oo loomenye, neiborrie onyek aarubare nkaitin oo ltung'ana leina kop apa naaidaikie Enkai te dukuya ninche. 
26   Ore enkaraki ina neputu Enkai e Israel oltau le Puul, olaiguanani le Asiria, o ltau le Tilgal-Pilnesa, olaiguanani le Asiria, nearaa ninche meshomo, aa taa ile Ruben o le Gad, o lpisiaai loo ltung'ana le Manase, nereu ninche Hala, o Habor, o Hara, nereu sii olkeju le Gosan ometabaiki ena olong.

